out0 = spark.sql(f"""
    with mysub as (
  SELECT
    'F4211' AS SRC_TBL_NM,
    F4211.SDDOC AS DELV_NUM,
    F4211.SDLNID AS DELV_LINE_NBR,
    F4211.SDDCTO AS DELV_TYP_CD,
    F4211.SDKCOO AS CO_CD,
    NULL AS MATL_SHRT_DESC,
    NULL AS MATL_MVMT_TYPE_CD,
    F4211.SDDOCO AS DOC_REF_NUM,
    NULL AS PICK_CNTL_STS_CD,
    NULL AS LINE_ITEM_CAT_CD,
    NULL AS SPL_STK_TYPE_CD,
    NULL AS PARNT_BTCH_SPLT_CNTR_NBR,
    NULL AS PARNT_BOM_CNTR_NBR,
    NULL AS FCTR_NMRTR_MEAS,
    NULL AS FCTR_DNMNTR_MEAS,
    NULL AS ACTL_GI_DTTM,
    CAST (TRIM (F4211.SDSOQS) AS DECIMAL(18, 4)) AS ACTL_SLS_UNIT_DELV_QTY,
    NULL AS ACTL_SKU_DELV_QTY,
    NULL AS BASE_UOM_CD,
    TRIM (F4211.SDLOTN) AS BTCH_NUM,
    NULL AS BILL_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS CNFRM_STS_CD,
    NULL AS MFG_DTTM,
    NULL AS DELV_BILL_STS_CD,
    NULL AS DELV_CMPLT_IND,
    NULL AS DELV_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS DELV_STS_CD,
    NULL AS DELV_TOT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS EXP_DTTM,
    NULL AS GM_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS GM_STS_CD,
    NULL AS INTCO_BILL_STS_CD,
    TRIM (F4211.SDLITM) AS MATL_NUM,
    NULL AS ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS NUM_OF_CNTNRS_CNT,
    NULL AS ORDR_BILL_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PACK_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PACK_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PICK_CNFRM_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PICK_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PICK_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PRC_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PRCSG_TOT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS RECV_PLNT_CD,
    NULL AS REF_STS_CD,
    NULL AS REF_TOT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS REJ_STS_CD,
    TRIM (F4211.SDLNID) AS SLS_ORDR_LINE_NBR_REF,
    NULL AS SLS_ORDR_TYPE_CD,
    TRIM (F4211.SDUOM) AS SLS_UOM_CD,
    TRIM (F4211.SDMCU) AS SHIPPING_PLNT_CD,
    TRIM (F4211.SDLOCN) AS SLOC_CD,
    NULL AS VEND_BTCH_NUM,
    NULL AS WM_STS_CD,
    NULL AS CRT_DTTM,
    NULL AS ITM_TYPE,
    NULL AS ITM_OF_REF_DOC,
    NULL AS GRS_WT_MEAS,
    NULL AS NET_WT_MEAS,
    NULL AS WT_UOM_CD,
    NULL AS VOL_MEAS,
    NULL AS VOL_UOM_CD,
    NULL AS NET_VAL_AMT,
    NULL AS PROD_HIER_CD,
    NULL AS MATL_GRP_4,
    NULL AS MATL_GRP_4_DESC,
    NULL AS DSTR_CHNL_CD,
    NULL AS ITM_BILL_BLK_STS_CD,
    NULL AS ITM_OVRL_DELV_BLK_STS_CD,
    NULL AS ENT_MATL_NUM,
    NULL AS DIVISION_CD,
    NULL AS DOC_CAT_SD,
    NULL AS MATL_GRP_CD,
    NULL AS MATL_TYPE_CD,
    NULL AS CUM_BTCH_QTY,
    F4211.SDSFXO AS ORDR_SFX,
    null AS MATCH_TYPE,
    TRIM (F4211.SDLNTY) AS LINE_TYPE_DELV,
 NULL AS ORIG_QTY_DELV_ITM
  from
    {Config.sourceDatabase}.F4211 F4211
  where
    F4211._deleted_ = 'F'
  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'F43121' AS SRC_TBL_NM,
    F43121.PRDOC AS DELV_NUM,
    CONCAT(F43121.PRLNID, \" \", F43121.PRNLIN) AS DELV_LINE_NBR,
    F43121.PRDCTO AS DELV_TYP_CD,
    F43121.PRKCOO AS CO_CD,
    NULL AS MATL_SHRT_DESC,
    NULL AS MATL_MVMT_TYPE_CD,
    F43121.PRDOCO AS DOC_REF_NUM,
    NULL AS PICK_CNTL_STS_CD,
    NULL AS LINE_ITEM_CAT_CD,
    NULL AS SPL_STK_TYPE_CD,
    NULL AS PARNT_BTCH_SPLT_CNTR_NBR,
    NULL AS PARNT_BOM_CNTR_NBR,
    NULL AS FCTR_NMRTR_MEAS,
    NULL AS FCTR_DNMNTR_MEAS,
    NULL AS ACTL_GI_DTTM,
    CAST (TRIM (F43121.PRUREC) AS DECIMAL(18, 4)) AS ACTL_SLS_UNIT_DELV_QTY,
    NULL AS ACTL_SKU_DELV_QTY,
    NULL AS BASE_UOM_CD,
    TRIM (F43121.PRLOTN) AS BTCH_NUM,
    NULL AS BILL_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS CNFRM_STS_CD,
    NULL AS MFG_DTTM,
    NULL AS DELV_BILL_STS_CD,
    NULL AS DELV_CMPLT_IND,
    NULL AS DELV_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS DELV_STS_CD,
    NULL AS DELV_TOT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS EXP_DTTM,
    NULL AS GM_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS GM_STS_CD,
    NULL AS INTCO_BILL_STS_CD,
    TRIM (F43121.PRLITM) AS MATL_NUM,
    NULL AS ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS NUM_OF_CNTNRS_CNT,
    NULL AS ORDR_BILL_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PACK_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PACK_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PICK_CNFRM_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PICK_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PICK_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PRC_ICMPT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS PRCSG_TOT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS RECV_PLNT_CD,
    NULL AS REF_STS_CD,
    NULL AS REF_TOT_STS_CD,
    NULL AS REJ_STS_CD,
    TRIM (F43121.PRLNID) AS SLS_ORDR_LINE_NBR_REF,
    NULL AS SLS_ORDR_TYPE_CD,
    TRIM (F43121.PRUOM) AS SLS_UOM_CD,
    TRIM (F43121.PRMCU) AS SHIPPING_PLNT_CD,
    TRIM (F43121.PRLOCN) AS SLOC_CD,
    NULL AS VEND_BTCH_NUM,
    NULL AS WM_STS_CD,
    NULL AS CRT_DTTM,
    NULL AS ITM_TYPE,
    NULL AS ITM_OF_REF_DOC,
    NULL AS GRS_WT_MEAS,
    NULL AS NET_WT_MEAS,
    NULL AS WT_UOM_CD,
    NULL AS VOL_MEAS,
    NULL AS VOL_UOM_CD,
    NULL AS NET_VAL_AMT,
    NULL AS PROD_HIER_CD,
    NULL AS MATL_GRP_4,
    NULL AS MATL_GRP_4_DESC,
    NULL AS DSTR_CHNL_CD,
    NULL AS ITM_BILL_BLK_STS_CD,
    NULL AS ITM_OVRL_DELV_BLK_STS_CD,
    NULL AS ENT_MATL_NUM,
    NULL AS DIVISION_CD,
    NULL AS DOC_CAT_SD,
    NULL AS MATL_GRP_CD,
    NULL AS MATL_TYPE_CD,
    NULL AS CUM_BTCH_QTY,
    F43121.PRSFXO AS ORDR_SFX,
    F43121.PRMATC AS MATCH_TYPE,
    TRIM (F43121.PRLNTY) AS LINE_TYPE_DELV,
 NULL AS ORIG_QTY_DELV_ITM
  from
    {Config.sourceDatabase}.F43121 F43121
  where
    F43121._deleted_ = 'F'
)
SELECT
  SRC_SYS_CD,
  DELV_NUM,
  DELV_LINE_NBR,
  DELV_TYP_CD,
  CO_CD,
  MATL_SHRT_DESC,
  MATL_MVMT_TYPE_CD,
  DOC_REF_NUM,
  PICK_CNTL_STS_CD,
  LINE_ITEM_CAT_CD,
  SPL_STK_TYPE_CD,
  PARNT_BTCH_SPLT_CNTR_NBR,
  PARNT_BOM_CNTR_NBR,
  FCTR_NMRTR_MEAS,
  FCTR_DNMNTR_MEAS,
  ACTL_GI_DTTM,
  ACTL_SLS_UNIT_DELV_QTY,
  ACTL_SKU_DELV_QTY,
  BASE_UOM_CD,
  BTCH_NUM,
  BILL_ICMPT_STS_CD,
  CNFRM_STS_CD,
  MFG_DTTM,
  DELV_BILL_STS_CD,
  DELV_CMPLT_IND,
  DELV_ICMPT_STS_CD,
  DELV_STS_CD,
  DELV_TOT_STS_CD,
  EXP_DTTM,
  GM_ICMPT_STS_CD,
  GM_STS_CD,
  INTCO_BILL_STS_CD,
  MATL_NUM,
  ICMPT_STS_CD,
  NUM_OF_CNTNRS_CNT,
  ORDR_BILL_STS_CD,
  PACK_ICMPT_STS_CD,
  PACK_STS_CD,
  PICK_CNFRM_STS_CD,
  PICK_ICMPT_STS_CD,
  PICK_STS_CD,
  PRC_ICMPT_STS_CD,
  PRCSG_TOT_STS_CD,
  RECV_PLNT_CD,
  REF_STS_CD,
  REF_TOT_STS_CD,
  REJ_STS_CD,
  SLS_ORDR_LINE_NBR_REF,
  SLS_ORDR_TYPE_CD,
  SLS_UOM_CD,
  SHIPPING_PLNT_CD,
  SLOC_CD,
  VEND_BTCH_NUM,
  WM_STS_CD,
  CRT_DTTM,
  ITM_TYPE,
  ITM_OF_REF_DOC,
  GRS_WT_MEAS,
  NET_WT_MEAS,
  WT_UOM_CD,
  VOL_MEAS,
  VOL_UOM_CD,
  NET_VAL_AMT,
  PROD_HIER_CD,
  MATL_GRP_4,
  MATL_GRP_4_DESC,
  DSTR_CHNL_CD,
  ITM_BILL_BLK_STS_CD,
  ITM_OVRL_DELV_BLK_STS_CD,
  ENT_MATL_NUM,
  DIVISION_CD,
  DOC_CAT_SD,
  MATL_GRP_CD,
  MATL_TYPE_CD,
  CUM_BTCH_QTY,
  ORDR_SFX,
  MATCH_TYPE,
  LINE_TYPE_DELV,
  SRC_TBL_NM,
  ORIG_QTY_DELV_ITM
FROM
  (
    select
      *,
      ROW_NUMBER() over (
        partition by SRC_SYS_CD,
        DELV_NUM,
        DELV_LINE_NBR,
        DELV_TYP_CD,
        CO_CD,
        DOC_REF_NUM,
        ORDR_SFX,
        MATCH_TYPE,
        SRC_TBL_NM
        order by
          DELV_LINE_NBR
      ) as rnk
    from(
        SELECT
          DISTINCT '{Config.sourceSystem}'   AS SRC_SYS_CD,
          mysub.DELV_NUM AS DELV_NUM,
          mysub.DELV_LINE_NBR AS DELV_LINE_NBR,
          mysub.DELV_TYP_CD AS DELV_TYP_CD,
          mysub.CO_CD AS CO_CD,
          mysub.MATL_SHRT_DESC AS MATL_SHRT_DESC,
          mysub.MATL_MVMT_TYPE_CD AS MATL_MVMT_TYPE_CD,
          mysub.DOC_REF_NUM AS DOC_REF_NUM,
          mysub.PICK_CNTL_STS_CD AS PICK_CNTL_STS_CD,
          mysub.LINE_ITEM_CAT_CD AS LINE_ITEM_CAT_CD,
          mysub.SPL_STK_TYPE_CD AS SPL_STK_TYPE_CD,
          mysub.PARNT_BTCH_SPLT_CNTR_NBR AS PARNT_BTCH_SPLT_CNTR_NBR,
          mysub.PARNT_BOM_CNTR_NBR AS PARNT_BOM_CNTR_NBR,
          mysub.FCTR_NMRTR_MEAS AS FCTR_NMRTR_MEAS,
          mysub.FCTR_DNMNTR_MEAS AS FCTR_DNMNTR_MEAS,
          mysub.ACTL_GI_DTTM AS ACTL_GI_DTTM,
          CAST (mysub.ACTL_SLS_UNIT_DELV_QTY AS DECIMAL(18, 4)) AS ACTL_SLS_UNIT_DELV_QTY,
          mysub.ACTL_SKU_DELV_QTY AS ACTL_SKU_DELV_QTY,
          mysub.BASE_UOM_CD AS BASE_UOM_CD,
          mysub.BTCH_NUM AS BTCH_NUM,
          mysub.BILL_ICMPT_STS_CD AS BILL_ICMPT_STS_CD,
          mysub.CNFRM_STS_CD AS CNFRM_STS_CD,
          mysub.MFG_DTTM AS MFG_DTTM,
          mysub.DELV_BILL_STS_CD AS DELV_BILL_STS_CD,
          mysub.DELV_CMPLT_IND AS DELV_CMPLT_IND,
          mysub.DELV_ICMPT_STS_CD AS DELV_ICMPT_STS_CD,
          mysub.DELV_STS_CD AS DELV_STS_CD,
          mysub.DELV_TOT_STS_CD AS DELV_TOT_STS_CD,
          mysub.EXP_DTTM AS EXP_DTTM,
          mysub.GM_ICMPT_STS_CD AS GM_ICMPT_STS_CD,
          mysub.GM_STS_CD AS GM_STS_CD,
          mysub.INTCO_BILL_STS_CD AS INTCO_BILL_STS_CD,
          mysub.MATL_NUM AS MATL_NUM,
          mysub.ICMPT_STS_CD AS ICMPT_STS_CD,
          mysub.NUM_OF_CNTNRS_CNT AS NUM_OF_CNTNRS_CNT,
          mysub.ORDR_BILL_STS_CD AS ORDR_BILL_STS_CD,
          mysub.PACK_ICMPT_STS_CD AS PACK_ICMPT_STS_CD,
          mysub.PACK_STS_CD AS PACK_STS_CD,
          mysub.PICK_CNFRM_STS_CD AS PICK_CNFRM_STS_CD,
          mysub.PICK_ICMPT_STS_CD AS PICK_ICMPT_STS_CD,
          mysub.PICK_STS_CD AS PICK_STS_CD,
          mysub.PRC_ICMPT_STS_CD AS PRC_ICMPT_STS_CD,
          mysub.PRCSG_TOT_STS_CD AS PRCSG_TOT_STS_CD,
          mysub.RECV_PLNT_CD AS RECV_PLNT_CD,
          mysub.REF_STS_CD AS REF_STS_CD,
          mysub.REF_TOT_STS_CD AS REF_TOT_STS_CD,
          mysub.REJ_STS_CD AS REJ_STS_CD,
          mysub.SLS_ORDR_LINE_NBR_REF AS SLS_ORDR_LINE_NBR_REF,
          mysub.SLS_ORDR_TYPE_CD AS SLS_ORDR_TYPE_CD,
          mysub.SLS_UOM_CD AS SLS_UOM_CD,
          mysub.SHIPPING_PLNT_CD AS SHIPPING_PLNT_CD,
          mysub.SLOC_CD AS SLOC_CD,
          mysub.VEND_BTCH_NUM AS VEND_BTCH_NUM,
          mysub.WM_STS_CD AS WM_STS_CD,
          mysub.CRT_DTTM AS CRT_DTTM,
          mysub.ITM_TYPE AS ITM_TYPE,
          mysub.ITM_OF_REF_DOC AS ITM_OF_REF_DOC,
          mysub.GRS_WT_MEAS AS GRS_WT_MEAS,
          mysub.NET_WT_MEAS AS NET_WT_MEAS,
          mysub.WT_UOM_CD AS WT_UOM_CD,
          mysub.VOL_MEAS AS VOL_MEAS,
          mysub.VOL_UOM_CD AS VOL_UOM_CD,
          mysub.NET_VAL_AMT AS NET_VAL_AMT,
          mysub.PROD_HIER_CD AS PROD_HIER_CD,
          mysub.MATL_GRP_4 AS MATL_GRP_4,
          mysub.MATL_GRP_4_DESC AS MATL_GRP_4_DESC,
          mysub.DSTR_CHNL_CD AS DSTR_CHNL_CD,
          mysub.ITM_BILL_BLK_STS_CD AS ITM_BILL_BLK_STS_CD,
          mysub.ITM_OVRL_DELV_BLK_STS_CD AS ITM_OVRL_DELV_BLK_STS_CD,
          mysub.ENT_MATL_NUM AS ENT_MATL_NUM,
          mysub.DIVISION_CD AS DIVISION_CD,
          mysub.DOC_CAT_SD AS DOC_CAT_SD,
          mysub.MATL_GRP_CD AS MATL_GRP_CD,
          mysub.MATL_TYPE_CD AS MATL_TYPE_CD,
          mysub.CUM_BTCH_QTY AS CUM_BTCH_QTY,
          mysub.ORDR_SFX AS ORDR_SFX,
          COALESCE(mysub.MATCH_TYPE, 'NULL') AS MATCH_TYPE,
          mysub.LINE_TYPE_DELV AS LINE_TYPE_DELV,
          mysub.SRC_TBL_NM AS SRC_TBL_NM,
    mysub.ORIG_QTY_DELV_ITM AS ORIG_QTY_DELV_ITM
        from
          mysub mysub
      )
  )
WHERE
  rnk = 1  
 
""")
